    <span>Scroll</span>
    <div class="scroll-bar"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="gold-line">

<!-- MANIFESTO -->
<div class="manifesto">
  <div class="manifesto-inner">
    <p class="manifesto-line">Instagram disappears.</p>
    <span class="manifesto-dot"></span>
    <p class="manifesto-line">Facebook closes accounts.</p>
    <span class="manifesto-dot"></span>
    <p class="manifesto-line">Newspapers don't write about everyday families.</p>
    <span class="manifesto-dot"></span>
    <p class="manifesto-line gold">My Legacy Continues does.</p>
    <span class="manifesto-dot"></span>
    <p class="manifesto-line bright">One purchase. No subscriptions. Permanent.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<hr class="gold-line">

<!-- FOUR PILLARS -->
<section class="pillars" id="pillars">
  <div class="pillars-header">
    <span class="eyebrow">The Platform</span>
    <h2 class="section-hed">Four Pillars. One Mission.</h2>
    <p class="section-dek">Every life gets a permanent home. This is the infrastructure that keeps your story alive.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="pillar pillar-1">
    <div class="pillar-bg"></div>
    <div class="pillar-num-panel">
      <span class="pillar-roman">I</span>
    </div>
    <div class="pillar-content">
      <span class="pillar-tag">Human Legacy</span>
      <h3 class="pillar-title">Your Family's Story,<br>Written Forever</h3>
      <p class="pillar-body">Heritage Culture Books. Family profiles. Memorial pages. We dig into the archives — census records, border crossings, Spanish nobility lines — and build a record your grandchildren's grandchildren will still be reading. Nobody does this at the community level for everyday families.</p>
      <a href="heritage-book.html" class="pillar-link">Start Your Heritage Book</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="pillar pillar-2">
    <div class="pillar-bg"></div>
    <div class="pillar-num-panel">
      <span class="pillar-roman">II</span>
    </div>
    <div class="pillar-content">
      <span class="pillar-tag">Business Legacy</span>
      <h3 class="pillar-title">Your Work Deserves<br>a Real Story</h3>
      <p class="pillar-body">Contractors, tradespeople, small business owners — you built something real with your hands. A QR code on your truck, your business card, your job sign. Scan it and they see 20 years of work, your best jobs, your story. Bears Concrete is the demo. McNeal Construction is proof.</p>
      <a href="business-profile.html" class="pillar-link">Build Your Business Profile</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="pillar pillar-3">
    <div class="pillar-bg"></div>
    <div class="pillar-num-panel">
      <span class="pillar-roman">III</span>
    </div>
    <div class="pillar-content">
      <span class="pillar-tag">Animal Legacy</span>
      <h3 class="pillar-title">Every Pet Gets<br>a Permanent Record</h3>
      <p class="pillar-body">From intake to forever home to memorial — every rescue dog gets a permanent profile, free. The QR tag connects the physical world to the digital story. Shoshi and Underdog Heroes is our first real partner. Scan the collar and the whole life opens up.</p>
      <a href="rescue-registry.html" class="pillar-link">View the Rescue Registry</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="pillar pillar-4">
    <div class="pillar-bg"></div>
    <div class="pillar-num-panel">
      <span class="pillar-roman">IV</span>
    </div>
    <div class="pillar-content">
      <span class="pillar-tag">Community Legacy</span>
      <h3 class="pillar-title">Build the Infrastructure.<br>Own the Story.</h3>
      <p class="pillar-body">Neighborhoods. Churches. Cultural groups. Entire communities preserving their collective story in one permanent place. The Vector90 inspiration. The Nipsey blueprint. We're building the foundation right now in Santa Maria — and the platform goes long-term from here.</p>
      <a href="#" class="pillar-link">Coming 2026</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="gold-line">

<!-- PRODUCTS -->
<section class="products" id="products">
  <div class="products-inner">
    <div class="products-header">
      <span class="eyebrow">What We Build</span>
      <h2 class="section-hed">One Purchase. Permanent Record.</h2>
      <p class="section-dek">Every product creates a profile linked to a QR code. No renewals. No login to view. Just a story that never disappears.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="products-grid">

      <div class="product-tile">
        <span class="tile-tag">Human Legacy</span>
        <div class="tile-name">Heritage Culture Book</div>
        <div class="tile-tagline">Your Family's Story, Researched and Written</div>
        <p class="tile-desc">We dig into the archives — FamilySearch, Spanish nobility records, border crossings, census records — and write your family's story chapter by chapter. Not a template. A real book.</p>
        <ul class="tile-bullets">
          <li>Professional genealogy research — 4 generations minimum</li>
          <li>Custom written narrative, not a template</li>
          <li>Family timeline and migration map</li>
          <li>Physical book printed and shipped</li>
          <li>Permanent digital profile with QR code</li>
          <li>English and Spanish available</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="tile-price">$199</div>
        <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/bJe14o2a35pO6csg16fQI02" class="btn-shine btn-primary-gold">Order Heritage Book</a>
      </div>

      <div class="product-tile">
        <span class="tile-tag">Memorial</span>
        <div class="tile-name">Cemetery Memorial QR Plaque</div>
        <div class="tile-tagline">Give Them a Voice at the Gravesite</div>
        <p class="tile-desc">A stainless steel QR plaque attaches to any headstone. Scan to hear their songs, see photos, leave voice tributes. Not mourning. Visiting.</p>
        <ul class="tile-bullets">
          <li>Stainless steel — weatherproof, permanent adhesive</li>
          <li>We build the memorial profile for you</li>
          <li>Photo and video gallery</li>
          <li>Tribute wall — family leaves messages</li>
          <li>Remembrance Mode on birthdays</li>
          <li>English and Spanish on every profile</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="tile-price">$129</div>
        <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/6oU3cw15Z5pO7gw5msfQI06" class="btn-shine btn-primary-gold">Order Memorial Plaque</a>
      </div>

      <div class="product-tile">
        <span class="tile-tag">Animal Legacy</span>
        <div class="tile-name">Pet QR Legacy Tag</div>
        <div class="tile-tagline">If They Get Lost, This Brings Them Home</div>
        <p class="tile-desc">A durable metal QR tag for your pet's collar. Scan to see contact info, medical needs, and how to reach you — no app required.</p>
        <ul class="tile-bullets">
          <li>Scan instantly — no app needed</li>
          <li>Owner contact shown — your number stays private</li>
          <li>Medical info: medications, allergies, vet contact</li>
          <li>Personality notes for finders</li>
          <li>Links to your family's legacy profile</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="tile-btn-row">
          <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/eVq7sM9CvdWk9oE4iofQI07" class="btn-shine btn-primary-gold">Basic — $24.99</a>
          <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/bJe28s15ZcSgdEU9CIfQI09" class="btn-shine btn-ghost">Premium — $49.99</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="product-tile">
        <span class="tile-tag">Business Legacy</span>
        <div class="tile-name">Business Founder Profile</div>
        <div class="tile-tagline">Your Business Card Should Tell the Whole Story</div>
        <p class="tile-desc">Scan your card and they see your real story — 20 years of work, your best jobs, your license number, and why you started. Done for you. Permanent.</p>
        <ul class="tile-bullets">
          <li>We write your founder story for you</li>
          <li>Portfolio of your best work — up to 10 photos</li>
          <li>Tap-to-call and quote request built in</li>
          <li>License number and certifications displayed</li>
          <li>QR code for cards, truck decals, job signs</li>
