<!-- ORIGIN -->
<section class="origin" id="about">
  <div class="origin-inner">
    <div class="origin-text">
      <span class="eyebrow">Our Story</span>
      <h2 class="origin-title">Most families lose<br>their history.</h2>
      <p class="origin-p">Not because they don't care. Because nobody built a system to hold it. Papers get thrown out. Grandparents die before they're recorded. The family line fades one generation at a time.</p>
      <p class="origin-p"><strong>We started My Legacy Continues in Santa Maria</strong> because we almost lost ours. The Vazquez family line goes back to <strong>1547 in Galicia, Spain</strong> — a confirmed hidalgo line from the Reconquista. That almost disappeared too.</p>
      <p class="origin-p">Every product we build exists to make sure that doesn't happen to your family. Physical. Digital. Permanent. No subscription required.</p>
      <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/bJe14o2a35pO6csg16fQI02" class="btn-shine btn-primary-gold" style="margin-top:8px;">Start With the Heritage Book — $199</a>
    </div>
